description:
A TV show is turning the children of Fort Nightingale into zombies - but that's not the weirdest thing going on in the city! All of the adults have fallen into a stupor, their bodies motionless like living dolls. Could these strange episodes be linked to the disappearance of a nuclear bomb? And how are the orphans with glowing eyes connected to these events?
